===Etymology===
Modern Latin, from {{AGr.}} '''{{polytonic|[[ἥλιος]]}}''' ‘sun’ (because its presence was first theorised in the sun's atmosphere).

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|hē'lēəm}}, {{IPA|/ˈhiːlɪəm/}}, {{SAMPA|/"hi:li@m/}}

===Hyphenation===
