===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|-}}

# A [[colorless]] and [[inert]] gas, and the second lightest chemical [[element]] (''symbol'' He) with an [[atomic number]] of 2 and [[atomic weight]] of 4.002602.

